lead_paragraph: A man who set off a bomb was sucked out of a Daallo Airlines plane through a hole when the blast ripped open the cabin in flight, officials said.

headline.print_headline: Shabab Claim Bid to Blow Up Jet

snippet: A man who set off a bomb was sucked out of a Daallo Airlines plane through a hole when the blast ripped open the cabin in flight, officials said.
abstract: Somalia's Shabab insurgents claim responsibility for blast that tore hole in plane, prompting emergency landing in Mogadishu.
